Bad Ink - Season 1, Episode 10





Tramp Stamps Gone Wild

Jeremy had an obsession with sea monkeys that led to his decision to get a life altering tramp stamp he now regrets. Dirk and Ruckus have seen their fair share of tramp stamps, but a "man stamp"? This is new territory for them.

They get a call to help a grandmother who turns out to have a wild streak and a wild past. SJ is not your typical grandma and her tattoo is just as wild.




Original Air Date: 15-Sep-2013
